{"tid":1002470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警再掃黑幫避風塘　扣七艇拘兩男","createTime":"2019-01-31T03:19:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T07:47:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"632ce34330e000badc6d450f7d55a175425bd8b2","tid":1002470,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T03:19:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190131/20603191\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190131%2F20603191&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6i2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=7a6ac613\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190131%2F20603191&h=f1b0b72b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190131/20603191</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月31日 <br />\n<br />\n警再掃黑幫避風塘　扣七艇拘兩男<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190131/large/31la5p04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190131%2Flarge%2F31la5p04.jpg&h=47b2a58e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水警人員將涉嫌違規的快艇拖走調查。劉永明攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】《蘋果》早前揭發五大黑幫爭奪各避風塘海上泊位出租圖利，警方連串掃蕩後，昨日東九龍總區、水警總區、港島總區、有組織罪案及三合會調查科、機動部隊及海事處人員，進行第六次代號「先行者」反罪惡行動，巡查觀塘、香港仔、筲箕灣及長洲避風塘，拘捕兩名涉嫌勒索及刑事毀壞案男子，並扣押七艘快艇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n涉淋油勒索遊艇泊位費<br />\n<br />\n被捕兩男子分別24及35歲，警方懷疑他們與去年10月28日觀塘避風塘發生的六艘遊艇被淋油及勒索案有關。被扣押七艘快艇，涉嫌違反商船（本地船隻）條例，沒有清晰展示船牌號碼、船隻沒領有證明書、違反牌照條件等，由水警總區港口分區跟進檢控。<br />\n<br />\n由去年11月起展開的「先行者」行動，警方至今共扣押九艘違反牌照規定或與案有關的快艇，拘捕六名男女（24至35歲），涉嫌干犯刑事毀壞、勒索和管有仿製槍械等罪行。另有16艘船涉嫌非法改裝或違反牌照條件，正由海事處跟進。<br />\n<br />\n多個黑幫為爭奪每月合共逾億元的非法海上泊位費，曾多次發生衝突，當中新義安觀塘派系，面對14K和聯英社入侵避風塘，曾高調海上晒馬。<br />\n<br />\n■記者劉永明  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n李偲嫣大嫂質疑警用過度武力"},{"pid":"2f1f0a66d612b329e836be56fad645905d7e185e","tid":1002470,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T04:05:32.000Z","msg":"放心 陸地有樊蛇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i6L5vh8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi6L5vh8.png&h=8ba47dd9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b61d3e50739888bf1393fc1d4835d4f9153f6df","tid":1002470,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T04:32:21.000Z","msg":"說好要做海賊王嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358521245b07f349ce3a2638c4ade20f24d4467b","tid":1002470,"uid":132461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T07:47:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}